                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='24023' id='32' type-v2='text' w='62143' x='36883' y='74609'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' underline='true'>INSIGHTS</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1.While on-time deliveries are highly concentrated around zero delay, late deliveries (orange) are more widely spread across higher delay values, indicating inconsistency and the presence of extreme delays in the system.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2.Approximately 6.8% of orders are delivered late, indicating overall stable but improvable performance.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>3.Freight cost does not show a strong correlation with delivery delay, suggesting higher shipping costs do not guarantee faster delivery.” </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#e15759' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&quot;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#e15759' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='8'>While overall delivery performance is stable, the presence of highly variable late deliveries suggests opportunities to improve consistency and reduce extreme delays.</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#e15759' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>&quot;</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='8' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zones>
        </devicelayout>
      </devicelayouts>
